{
  "text": "As we will see below, much can be learned from the SCGF about the probability of the currents, but in the rest of this section we remind the reader about some fluctuation relations which will be discussed later in the paper. At this point it is possible to use the LDP (4) to rewrite the fluctuation relation [CITATION_1] in terms of the RF aŝ",
